{
  "stem": "6719.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not really.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Um, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] no, I--I-- I--I-- I wouldn't say something that's-- that's significant, but um-- um-- you know, toward the end of 19 hundred and 44, we heard, and actually saw-- witnessed-- some people being gathered up and put on transports to go somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes there was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, there was one-- one story that-- that's really funny.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Funny?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In a very macabre way, it's funny.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when I worked in Canada, we had a--a--a-- a toilet, which was two holes in the ground, and it had a blanket in front of it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it was like a--a-- a square box, OK?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And uh, there was a man down there that was in charge of that thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was a prisoner like us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He didn't like it that he had to work down there, because he-- he had to rely on us to give him food, or whatever it is, or whatever we found.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had a nickname.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He used to be called the Scheissmeister, which means, you know, the master of the crap house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And his name was Schepsel, and he came from-- I think he came from, I don't know, Russia or Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a Ludwik, as they called them, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I met him after the war in Salzburg, after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And uh, the reason that he was the master of the-- the Scheissmeister-- of the crap house was that he had to see that nobody stays there too long.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So, you see, there's only one way that you could do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You just dropped your pants, and you went, you know, onto your knees.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was no--no-- no seat or anything like that, and that's how you let go.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
